  },
  {
    "elementType": "p",
    "contents": "<p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"MPParagraphElement:DBD9D13F-B41C-45C5-B9DA-75A1AC29F189\" class=\"MPElement\" data-object-type=\"MPParagraphElement\">Note: In the last column, figures in brackets represent the percentage of each type of support in the total of support measures. Figures in brackets in the second last row represent the percentage of low, lower-middle, upper-middle and high-income countries that adopted support measures. The different instruments in each type of support used by countries are presented in the annex.</p>",
    "placeholderInnerHTML": "",
