    "contents": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"footnote-text\" id=\"MPFootnote:F0A4F5F9-30A6-443A-8085-AE242885F85E\" data-kind=\"footnote\"><p id=\"MPParagraphElement:0D403B02-DC3E-44D4-B00F-866944BCCC08\">Washington Post, 12 May 2020: <i>Small business used to define America’s economy. The pandemic could change that forever.</i></p></div>",
